Interface RunnableFuture<V>

    public interface RunnableFuture<V>
extends java.lang.Runnable, java.util.concurrent.Future<V>
    A Future that is Runnable. This class exists for Java 1.5 compatibility. When we switch to Java 1.6, this class should be removed and replaced by RunnableFuture.
